The '''''Florida State University Business Review''''' is a [[Law review|legal journal]] published at the [[Florida State University College of Law]]. It was founded in 2000 to provide a scholarly forum for contemporary legal discourse and to address the issues and concerns transforming the business community. It is generally recognized among the top 10 business reviews in the [[United States|US]] based on citations. [http://lawlib.wlu.edu/LJ/index2006.aspx]{{Dead link|date=December 2017}} The current [[Editor-in-chief|Editors-in-Chief]] are C. Alex Weaver and Eric S. Pendergraft.


